{"word":"G4292 - προκαλέομαι - prokaléomai - prok-al-eh'-om-ahee - Provoke","slug":"G4292","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προκαλέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prokaléomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>prok-al-eh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Provoke"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - prokaleomai</b> - <i>prok-al-eh'-om-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>; to <i>call forth to oneself</i> (<i>challenge</i>), that is, (by implication) to <i>irritate:</i> - provoke."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479\">G479</a>"}]}